Package: encodeUtils
Type: Package
Title: Query and Retrieve ENCODE Portal Metadata and Files
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: person(
    given = "Zoheb",
    family = "Khan",
    email = "zohebkhan600@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
Description: Provides a small R interface for querying the ENCODE Portal REST
    API, inspecting experiment and file metadata, and deliberately retrieving
    selected public datasets. The package is designed around ENCODE's search,
    matrix, report, object, file, and schema endpoints while keeping results
    easy to inspect from the R console. Downloads and local file loading are
    intended to be explicit, size-aware, cache-aware, and compatible with
    Bioconductor workflows.
License: Artistic-2.0
